Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:24.30,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the skies that are still unknown to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.40,Default,op,0,0,0,,I know, you're doing just the same -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.98,Default,op,0,0,0,,Dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.24,Default,op,0,0,0,,Just a small glow\NFrom those great days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.12,Default,op,0,0,0,,Is what dragging you along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.87,Default,op,0,0,0,,Giving you faith and some comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.79,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the sun that scorches badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:52.17,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only want to see your guise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.91,Default,op,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.18,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only watch \NWith tears on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:04.77,Default,op,0,0,0,,As you slowly disappear in this noon haze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,We're alone \NWe're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.31,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Walking this world on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.36,0:01:16.53,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Looking for each other since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.49,Default,op,0,0,0,,In the end, in the end, \NAfter the day we finally meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:27.00,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1\blur1\t(2100,2200,\shad3\blur3\c&HABADD8&)}We won't ever have to say "Goodbye"
Comment: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP END}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even more convinced now, I love you.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.56,0:02:11.56,Default,EP title,0,0,150,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HE3C4A2&\t(0,1100,\bord0.11\blur0.4\3c&H945431&)\c&HF7EEF0&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\fscx167\fscy157}Episode 2 \N\N\NMy 19th Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1200,0)}The sea, you say? \NSounds great...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I need to go to club every afternoon. \NThe "menu" has to be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? Coach Katsura returned to the temple. \NAnd a practice for girl can be done on the seaside as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The drama club is coming too. We rented a house by the sea. \NThere will also be 8 guys and 3 girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:34.85,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}House by the sea: 2 nights, 3 days
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see we have a shortage{ of girls} without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never get bored{/ weared}! \NEveryone is excited over the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really can't afford to be away for three days. \NI might get a call during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you getting a call from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,800)}You just said, "I might get a call while I'm away." \NWhom from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,10,,{\fade(700,0)\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Champion Takayuki becomes a pro
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play stupid now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm intrigued...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it can't be Coach Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Local train departs for Hashimoto at 14:54 from track 4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,900)}Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it in TV news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your announcement of becoming a pro.\NYour announcement of dropping out of university.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried so hard, but I couldn't reach you by phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They say Todo is now having the hardest times ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that. I tried calling you \Nbecause I don't think there's anything I can do for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we have not seen each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Oka Hiromi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a "Sports Toto" reporter, \Nand I hope you won't mind a quick interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Todo is the subject. \NYou both graduated from Nishi High, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We are writing a short biography of Todo. \NCollecting info from various sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but when we approached him for an interview today, \Nhe turned us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Approached him? \NYou mean you are aware of Todo's whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked for him tenaciously and it bore a fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you please tell me where Todo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! But take it easy, \Nwe're the ones interviewing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Todo, in fact
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,moved to one of the Buddhist shrines of Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the one he trusts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi? Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'm... \NI'm going to Coach Katsura's shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly needed his advice for my practices, therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go there this late? \NWon't you even have dinner with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you called him? \NSure you won't wake him up that late? {Sure you won't bother him with a sudden visit?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also raining now. \NMaybe it'd be better if you visit him tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the racket with your eyes. \NControl its movement tightly till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it still too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If your reach is further, \Nyou can handle the ball without leaving the baseline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For a Japan Open Champion this should be a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"No matter how pleasant was the touch of silk satin dress \Nto the skin, I just could not stand still here and cope with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too much scared of that person!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Ms. Wei{It's totally not Wei but a 'Wuy' surname sounds even more unnatural} from Yamashita, keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And now a letter from Shimano, \NMs. Keiko, class A of year 2. Let's read.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"I hate this thing called love."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"My sister is a traitor, and I am a fool! \NI don't want to see my sister! I only want to die."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to have made up his mind \Nto leave for America in about two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In two weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, he won't come back to Japan soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to fear, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the independent training?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the plan I drew for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here? You should be at "Park Hill" now, \Nperforming a weight training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here! I can't take it anymore! \NThis lonesome practice drives me crazy, but here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At Coach's place I can carry on training alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I will keep myself occupied every day here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka... Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am constantly busy here. \NI can't spare time to look after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's fine, you can stay in this temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you brought along two weeks' worth of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay in the room you lived in before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How most unexpected! \NI had no idea you are that skilled on piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Parents made me take lessons \Never since I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The piano was first, \Nbut then you switched to camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I could meet with Todo not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I informed him about your request for a meeting. \NHe is OK with that, you can visit him anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he now has his hands full \Nwith pro-test preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With Coach Katsura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Our mutual acquaintance told me where to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are going to see Todo... \NDo you mind if Ozaki and I accompany you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally I don't. \NBut what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To avert any injustice. {To serve him a defence.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Injustice? I'm going there merely to discuss Todo's announcement. \NI just want to know his view of it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly, \Nthe idea of becoming a pro is detestable to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You rejected every contract from major sponsors, \Nand refused to become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a matter of my personal judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me then, what do you want to hear? \NHow is this different for him? For his personal judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{There has been some misunderstanding, }You have some wrong ideas about me, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Ozaki are not the only ones to call him a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,During our days at Nishi High, \Nwe played countless matches in doubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of breath with just 2000 swings? \NThis way you would never win a full set.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to apply more strength, \Ntimings are also not even close to exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Power should have more sway over rocket \Nsince you're already an Overripe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An Overripe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He said Todo is an Overripe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo who is still in his early twenties is an overripe already... \NHow is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1250)}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}I see you're doing fine since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost count \Nhow many times I called your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,TV and newspapers were so solemn about you turning a pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my memory the image is still vivid of you, \Nlooking so hurt and broken that rainy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only later that I figured out you looked so lost then \Nbecause of all the worrying pondering about turning a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was so terribly worried. I had no idea what to do. \NI thought "I love Todo, and that's all that matters..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then someone told me you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have no idea why, or what for, \Nbut I came here because I didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine no matter what, Todo. \NThere's just this inexplicable trembling in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Coach, I brought this along. \NPlease treat yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, you too. \NHave some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So... This is a "Sports Drink." With orange, pine, peach...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about 1000 serves, 50 meters of shuttle run, \N5 kilometers of roadwork?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished already! \NI got up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to your room, \Nlet your body rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sports drink, want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Maki, \NI hope you enjoy your midsummer to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This nineteenth summer of my life \Nwill surely make a great memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because so far this summer \Nhas already became quite unforgettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us both take caution to not fall into unreserved drinking, eating and resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one way or another, for me this 19th summer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is special for so much reasons. {was so diversely eventful.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In ten years or so I could tell you the whole story...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for now. \NWholeheartedly yours, H.O."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I sought to see you \Nand the reason I needed to have a word with you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all the differences between us, \Nwe spent precious high school years on the same court.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please answer me sincerely, Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would one not be content with a once climbed peak? \NWhy would he climb it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean \N"be content with once climbed peak?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo is still in a good shape \Nand cannot be seen as a "player without future." {/ player for whom everything is in the past.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even knowing you'll get shattered to pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,even knowing that in the pro world \Nyou don't have a single chance to shine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you still advertently doom yourself to this. \NWhat for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Madame Butterfly! \N- Chiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us an answer, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please answer to me as to someone who climbed this peak along with you. {answer me the way one peak climber would answer another.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Katsura, you do, of course, \Nunderstand it as well as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, then, are you not making a single effort to stop Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you sending hopelessly Overripe Todo \Ninto the pit of the pro world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not force him. \NTodo chose this path himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly, I don't get it one bit! \NTodo is just 21 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like me, Todo started playing tennis \Nat the age of 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,From the age of 8, \Nwe were both spending our daylongs on the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make the idea clearer? \NIn middle school you become a regular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{Which means }During the 6 years of high school \Nyou're supposed to appear in players' top regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make the idea clearer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Speed of reflexes, instantaneous power, whole body strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In boxing it's the retiring age, \Nand tennis is no less harsh a sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to your senses \Nand see that the world's top is occupied by 10-odd players!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,While you may reach it by your mid-twenties at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The time when thirty-odd players \Ncould make it there is long gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays they are taught \Nto give their all to tennis since infancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that they reach their peak while still young, \Nand then leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but what if Todo could just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, you and I had a chance to become pros, \Nhad we started to aspire for it as long ago as back in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,when we were approaching our peak, \Nbut not now, when we're past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, our experience and techniques \Nwouldn't stand a single chance in the pro world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be ridiculed like a whipping boy! \NDon't you still get it, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this regardless?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still trying to do the impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For the same reason Coach Munakata then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,began teaching tennis to the newbie Oka \Nand not the experienced me, which drove me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a year older!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:18:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But only recently I realized \NI was already on my peak and had nowhere to rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt desolated...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Munakata's demeanor was so dignified, \NI used to loathe it back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, I love tennis no less than you do. \NTennis is my whole life, but I don't dare to become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As an amateur, you can forever keep playing at your comfortable pace, without having to part with tennis. That's how I see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am worried about you, with all my heart. \NLike a true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Madame Butterfly. Thank you. \NEverything you said was a gospel truth. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was full of determination to keep this to myself, \Nwithout ever telling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When Munakata Jin fell ill and retired from athletes, \Nhe was 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is my current age as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,had Mr. Munakata eluded his incurable disease, \Nwould he have continued his career unabated?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? \NThat is what bugs me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'd unleash on the world, \Nget involved in everything within his reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But then death called him. He left us while still young, \Nthat genius player of an unfortunate fate, Munakata Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I inherited his teachings, \NI had to follow that urge, whether I like it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as the one fortunately wielding a healthy body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though chances are, \NI will never be able to reach his level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At 21, he had to give up a player's life, \Nbut I'll try to finish what this man couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly said everything right. \NI am indeed already past my peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Munakata started playing tennis when he entered high school. \NBut I do it since 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of tennis, I might very well be an elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But that's what I believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in Mr. Munakata. \NIn what he saw with his own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold firmly to his way of life, \Nengraved on my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have already reached my peak once, \NI can certainly get there again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To drop out of university... \NTo announce transition to pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I hesitated, I was restless. \NBut I ultimately chose to go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now or never!\NEven now I still can and must achieve something! {If there's a certain point that I can reach if start walking now, I should go and try to reach it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For I don't want Munakata Jin to shrink \Nto just a fading{/ intangible} reminiscence! Not this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he lived while was still alive... \NI want to live this way too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Oka? \NI thought you were to stay for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'd better go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At such an important moment for him \NI don't want to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Todo will pass his pro-test brilliantly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever is ahead, \Nplease don't give up.
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:21.22,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:26.85,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.81,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings mixed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:32.69,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:37.88,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.79,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:50.17,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:57.05,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:03.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:12.66,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:17.86,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:20.91,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.95,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:29.48,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The day when Todo embarks on his long journey is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should not be sad about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We should keep our chins up!\NRight, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine, on the day of departure, Coach Katsura organizes \Na training match with Madame Butterfly. What a heartless coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.25,0:23:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You might run out of time to say goodbye to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:24:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: "Never Say Goodbye."
